title: Alanis Morissette Complete Disography
description:
I noticed that there was not a full Alanis discography to be found anywhere.  This is a collection of every album that I have been able to find by Alanis Morissette.  If I am missing anything, please, please, please, let me know.  I will be more than happy to find it and add it.  This is my first upload.

Includes the following albums:
Alanis
Now is the Time
The Prayer Cycle
Jagged Little Pill
Space Cakes
Supposed Former Infatuation Junkie
MTV Unplugged
Under Rug Swept
Feast On Scraps
Jagged Little Pill Acoustic
The Collection
So-Called Chaos
Live in Salt Lake City
Flavors of Entanglement (with bonus tracks)

Some of these files are from other people.  I do not remember who I got them from, but I appreciate them helping me to complete my collection and others complete theirs.  Enjoy.
